Bundled dependencies (also BSD-style, included under lib/):

- d3.min.js  — D3.js v3 by Mike Bostock (BSD-3-Clause)
- d3.geo.projection.min.js — D3 geographic projections (BSD-3-Clause)

Bundled data (also redistributable):

- stars.6.json, dsos.bright.json, dsos.6.json — based on HYG Database
  (CC BY-SA 2.5) and various Messier/NGC catalogs.
- constellations*.json — IAU constellation boundaries + Stellarium
  line-shape compilation.
- mw.json — Milky Way contours from the Stellarium data set.
- planets.json — planet positions / colours.

These data files are bundled here under the same terms d3-celestial
ships them upstream. BSD-3-Clause for the JS, CC BY-SA for the HYG-based
star data. NINA Headless redistributes both unmodified.
